&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://Amarantos-Arrebol.github.io/p/string-deep-copy-and-deep-assignment/%E6%B7%B1%E6%8B%B7%E8%B4%9D%E5%92%8C%E6%B7%B1%E8%B5%8B%E5%80%BC.assets/20250525132203978.png&#34;
